AB  - Some asymptotic tests for testing distributional assumptions, namely, the half-normal and truncated normal distributions for the stochastic frontier functions have been proposed. The tests are Lagrangean multiplier tests based on the Pearson family of truncated distributions. The statistics can be easily computed. Simple interpretations of the statistics and two empirical examples are provided.
